{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Both myself and my brother"},{"time":2000,"text":"belong to the under 30 demographic,"},{"time":4000,"text":"which Pat said makes 70 percent,"},{"time":6000,"text":"but according to our statistics"},{"time":8000,"text":"it makes 60 percent of the region's population."},{"time":11000,"text":"Qatar is no exception to the region."},{"time":13000,"text":"It's a very young nation led by young people."},{"time":16000,"text":"We have been reminiscing about the latest technologies"},{"time":19000,"text":"and the iPods,"},{"time":21000,"text":"and for me the abaya,"},{"time":23000,"text":"my traditional dress that I'm wearing today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25000,"text":"Now this is not a religious garment,"},{"time":27000,"text":"nor is it a religious statement."},{"time":29000,"text":"Instead, it's a diverse cultural statement"},{"time":32000,"text":"that we choose to wear."},{"time":34000,"text":"Now I remember a few years ago,"},{"time":36000,"text":"a journalist asked Dr. Sheikha, who's sitting here,"},{"time":39000,"text":"president of Qatar University --"},{"time":41000,"text":"who, by the way, is a woman --"},{"time":43000,"text":"he asked her whether she thought"},{"time":45000,"text":"the abaya hindered or infringed her freedom in any way."},{"time":48000,"text":"Her answer was quite the contrary."},{"time":50000,"text":"Instead, she felt more free,"},{"time":52000,"text":"more free because she could wear whatever she wanted"},{"time":54000,"text":"under the abaya."},{"time":56000,"text":"She could come to work in her pajamas and nobody would care."},{"time":59000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":61000,"text":"Not that you do; I'm just saying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"My point is here, people have a choice --"},{"time":67000,"text":"just like the Indian lady could wear her sari"},{"time":69000,"text":"or the Japanese woman could wear her kimono."},{"time":72000,"text":"We are changing our culture from within,"},{"time":74000,"text":"but at the same time"},{"time":76000,"text":"we are reconnecting with our traditions."},{"time":78000,"text":"We know that modernization is happening."},{"time":80000,"text":"And yes, Qatar wants to be a modern nation."},{"time":82000,"text":"But at the same time"},{"time":84000,"text":"we are reconnecting and reasserting our Arab heritage."},{"time":87000,"text":"It's important for us to grow organically."},{"time":90000,"text":"And we continuously make the conscious decision"},{"time":92000,"text":"to reach that balance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"In fact, research has shown"},{"time":97000,"text":"that the more the world is flat,"},{"time":99000,"text":"if I use Tom Friedman's analogy,"},{"time":101000,"text":"or global,"},{"time":103000,"text":"the more and more people are wanting to be different."},{"time":105000,"text":"And for us young people,"},{"time":107000,"text":"they're looking to become individuals"},{"time":109000,"text":"and find their differences amongst themselves."},{"time":111000,"text":"Which is why I prefer the Richard Wilk analogy"},{"time":114000,"text":"of globalizing the local"},{"time":116000,"text":"and localizing the global."},{"time":118000,"text":"We don't want to be all the same,"},{"time":120000,"text":"but we want to respect each other and understand each other."},{"time":123000,"text":"And therefore tradition becomes more important,"},{"time":125000,"text":"not less important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"Life necessitates a universal world,"},{"time":130000,"text":"however, we believe in the security"},{"time":132000,"text":"of having a local identity."},{"time":134000,"text":"And this is what the leaders of this region"},{"time":136000,"text":"are trying to do."},{"time":138000,"text":"We're trying to be part of this global village,"},{"time":140000,"text":"but at the same time we're revising ourselves"},{"time":143000,"text":"through our cultural institutions and cultural development."},{"time":147000,"text":"I'm a representation of that phenomenon."},{"time":150000,"text":"And I think a lot of people in this room,"},{"time":152000,"text":"I can see a lot of you are in the same position as myself."},{"time":154000,"text":"And I'm sure, although we can't see the people in Washington,"},{"time":157000,"text":"they are in the same position."},{"time":159000,"text":"We're continuously trying to straddle"},{"time":161000,"text":"different worlds, different cultures"},{"time":163000,"text":"and trying to meet the challenges"},{"time":165000,"text":"of a different expectation"},{"time":167000,"text":"from ourselves and from others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169000,"text":"So I want to ask a question:"},{"time":171000,"text":"What should culture in the 21st century look like?"},{"time":174000,"text":"In a time where the world is becoming personalized,"},{"time":177000,"text":"when the mobile phone, the burger, the telephone,"},{"time":180000,"text":"everything has its own personal identity,"},{"time":182000,"text":"how should we perceive ourselves"},{"time":184000,"text":"and how should we perceive others?"},{"time":186000,"text":"How does that impact our desert culture?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":189000,"text":"I'm not sure of how many of you in Washington"},{"time":192000,"text":"are aware of the cultural developments happening in the region"},{"time":195000,"text":"and, the more recent, Museum of Islamic Art"},{"time":197000,"text":"opened in Qatar in 2008."},{"time":200000,"text":"I myself am personalizing these cultural developments,"},{"time":203000,"text":"but I also understand"},{"time":205000,"text":"that this has to be done organically."},{"time":207000,"text":"Yes, we do have all the resources that we need"},{"time":210000,"text":"in order to develop new cultural institutions,"},{"time":213000,"text":"but what I think is more important"},{"time":215000,"text":"is that we are very fortunate"},{"time":217000,"text":"to have visionary leaders"},{"time":219000,"text":"who understand that this can't happen from outside,"},{"time":221000,"text":"it has to come from within."},{"time":223000,"text":"And guess what?"},{"time":225000,"text":"You might be surprised to know that most people in the Gulf"},{"time":228000,"text":"who are leading these cultural initiatives"},{"time":230000,"text":"happen to be women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232000,"text":"I want to ask you, why do you think this is?"},{"time":235000,"text":"Is it because it's a soft option;"},{"time":237000,"text":"we have nothing else to do?"},{"time":239000,"text":"No, I don't think so."},{"time":241000,"text":"I think that women in this part of the world"},{"time":244000,"text":"realize that culture is an important component"},{"time":246000,"text":"to connect people"},{"time":248000,"text":"both locally and regionally."},{"time":250000,"text":"It's a natural component"},{"time":252000,"text":"for bringing people together, discussing ideas --"},{"time":255000,"text":"in the same way we're doing here at TED."},{"time":257000,"text":"We're here, we're part of a community,"},{"time":259000,"text":"sharing out ideas and discussing them."},{"time":262000,"text":"Art becomes a very important part"},{"time":264000,"text":"of our national identity."},{"time":266000,"text":"The existential and social and political impact"},{"time":270000,"text":"an artist has"},{"time":272000,"text":"on his nation's development of cultural identity"},{"time":274000,"text":"is very important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276000,"text":"You know, art and culture is big business."},{"time":278000,"text":"Ask me."},{"time":280000,"text":"Ask the chairpersons and CEOs"},{"time":282000,"text":"of Sotheby's and Christie's."},{"time":284000,"text":"Ask Charles Saatchi about great art."},{"time":287000,"text":"They make a lot of money."},{"time":289000,"text":"So I think women in our society"},{"time":291000,"text":"are becoming leaders,"},{"time":293000,"text":"because they realize"},{"time":295000,"text":"that for their future generations,"},{"time":297000,"text":"it's very important"},{"time":299000,"text":"to maintain our cultural identities."},{"time":301000,"text":"Why else do Greeks demand the return"},{"time":303000,"text":"of the Elgin Marbles?"},{"time":305000,"text":"And why is there an uproar"},{"time":307000,"text":"when a private collector tries to sell his collection"},{"time":309000,"text":"to a foreign museum?"},{"time":311000,"text":"Why does it take me months on end"},{"time":313000,"text":"to get an export license from London or New York"},{"time":316000,"text":"in order to get pieces into my country?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"In few hours, Shirin Neshat, my friend from Iran"},{"time":322000,"text":"who's a very important artist for us"},{"time":325000,"text":"will be talking to you."},{"time":327000,"text":"She lives in New York City, but she doesn't try to be a Western artist."},{"time":330000,"text":"Instead, she tries to engage"},{"time":332000,"text":"in a very important dialogue"},{"time":334000,"text":"about her culture, nation and heritage."},{"time":336000,"text":"She does that through important visual forms"},{"time":339000,"text":"of photography and film."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"In the same way, Qatar is trying to grow its national museums"},{"time":345000,"text":"through an organic process from within."},{"time":348000,"text":"Our mission is of cultural integration and independence."},{"time":351000,"text":"We don't want to have what there is in the West."},{"time":353000,"text":"We don't want their collections."},{"time":355000,"text":"We want to build our own identities, our own fabric,"},{"time":358000,"text":"create an open dialogue"},{"time":360000,"text":"so that we share our ideas"},{"time":362000,"text":"and share yours with us."},{"time":364000,"text":"In a few days,"},{"time":366000,"text":"we will be opening the Arab Museum of Modern Art."},{"time":369000,"text":"We have done extensive research"},{"time":371000,"text":"to ensure that Arab and Muslim artists,"},{"time":373000,"text":"and Arabs who are not Muslims --"},{"time":375000,"text":"not all Arabs are Muslims, by the way --"},{"time":377000,"text":"but we make sure that they are represented"},{"time":379000,"text":"in this new institution."},{"time":382000,"text":"This institution is government-backed"},{"time":384000,"text":"and it has been the case"},{"time":386000,"text":"for the past three decades."},{"time":388000,"text":"We will open the museum in a few days,"},{"time":390000,"text":"and I welcome all of you to get on Qatar Airways"},{"time":393000,"text":"and come and join us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":395000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":397000,"text":"Now this museum is just as important to us as the West."},{"time":401000,"text":"Some of you might have heard"},{"time":403000,"text":"of the Algerian artist Baya Mahieddine,"},{"time":406000,"text":"but I doubt a lot of people know"},{"time":408000,"text":"that this artist worked in Picasso's studio"},{"time":411000,"text":"in Paris in the 1930s."},{"time":413000,"text":"For me it was a new discovery."},{"time":415000,"text":"And I think with time, in the years to come"},{"time":418000,"text":"we'll be learning a lot about our Picassos,"},{"time":420000,"text":"our Legers and our Cezannes."},{"time":422000,"text":"We do have artists,"},{"time":424000,"text":"but unfortunately we have not discovered them yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"Now visual expression is just one form"},{"time":430000,"text":"of culture integration."},{"time":433000,"text":"We have realized that recently"},{"time":435000,"text":"more and more people"},{"time":437000,"text":"are using the means of YouTube and social networking"},{"time":440000,"text":"to express their stories, share their photos"},{"time":443000,"text":"and tell their own stories through their own voices."},{"time":445000,"text":"In a similar way,"},{"time":447000,"text":"we have created the Doha Film Institute."},{"time":449000,"text":"Now the Doha Film Institute is an organization"},{"time":452000,"text":"to teach people about film and filmmaking."},{"time":455000,"text":"Last year we didn't have one Qatari woman filmmaker."},{"time":458000,"text":"Today I am proud to say"},{"time":460000,"text":"we have trained and educated"},{"time":462000,"text":"over 66 Qatari women filmmakers"},{"time":464000,"text":"to edit, tell their own stories"},{"time":466000,"text":"in their own voices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":474000,"text":"Now if you'll allow me, I would love to share a one-minute film"},{"time":477000,"text":"that has proven to show"},{"time":479000,"text":"that a 60-sec film can be as powerful as a haiku"},{"time":482000,"text":"in telling a big picture."},{"time":484000,"text":"And this is one of our filmmakers' products."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"(Video) Boy: Hey listen! Did you know that the stocks are up?"},{"time":490000,"text":"Who are you playing?"},{"time":492000,"text":"Girl: Uncle Khaled. Here, put on the headscarf."},{"time":494000,"text":"Khaled: Why would I want to put it on?"},{"time":496000,"text":"Girl: Do as you're told, young girl."},{"time":498000,"text":"Boy: No, you play mom and I play dad. (Girl: But it's my game.)"},{"time":501000,"text":"Play by yourself then."},{"time":503000,"text":"Girl: Women! One word and they get upset."},{"time":506000,"text":"Useless."},{"time":512000,"text":"Thank you. Thank you!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":516000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":523000,"text":"SM: Going back to straddling between East and West,"},{"time":526000,"text":"last month we had our second Doha Tribeca Film Festival"},{"time":529000,"text":"here in Doha."},{"time":531000,"text":"The Doha Tribeca Film Festival"},{"time":533000,"text":"was held at our new cultural hub, Katara."},{"time":536000,"text":"It attracted 42,000 people,"},{"time":538000,"text":"and we showcased 51 films."},{"time":540000,"text":"Now the Doha Tribeca Film Festival"},{"time":542000,"text":"is not an imported festival,"},{"time":544000,"text":"but rather an important festival"},{"time":546000,"text":"between the cities of New York and Doha."},{"time":549000,"text":"It's important for two things."},{"time":551000,"text":"First, it allows us to showcase"},{"time":553000,"text":"our Arab filmmakers and voices"},{"time":555000,"text":"to one of the most cosmopolitan cities in the world,"},{"time":557000,"text":"New York City."},{"time":559000,"text":"At the same time, we are inviting them"},{"time":561000,"text":"to come and explore our part of the world."},{"time":563000,"text":"They're learning our culture, our language, our heritage"},{"time":566000,"text":"and realizing we're just as different"},{"time":569000,"text":"and just the same as each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":572000,"text":"Now over and over again,"},{"time":574000,"text":"people have said, \"Let's build bridges,\""},{"time":576000,"text":"and frankly, I want to do more than that."},{"time":578000,"text":"I would like break the walls of ignorance"},{"time":580000,"text":"between East and West --"},{"time":582000,"text":"no, not the soft option that we have discussed before,"},{"time":585000,"text":"but rather the soft power"},{"time":587000,"text":"that Joseph Nye has spoken about before."},{"time":590000,"text":"Culture's a very important tool to bring people together."},{"time":593000,"text":"We should not underestimate it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596000,"text":"\"Know thyself,\""},{"time":598000,"text":"that is the journey of self-expression and self-realization"},{"time":600000,"text":"that we are traveling."},{"time":602000,"text":"Now I don't pretend to have all the answers,"},{"time":604000,"text":"but I know that me as an individual"},{"time":606000,"text":"and we as a nation"},{"time":608000,"text":"welcome this community"},{"time":610000,"text":"of ideas worth spreading."},{"time":612000,"text":"This is a very interesting journey."},{"time":614000,"text":"I welcome you on board"},{"time":616000,"text":"for us to engage and discuss new ideas"},{"time":619000,"text":"of how to bring people together"},{"time":621000,"text":"through cultural initiatives and discussions."},{"time":623000,"text":"Familiarity destroys and trumps fear. Try it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":627000,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, thank you very much. Shokran."}]},{"cues":[{"time":630000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}